                            <comment id="14607975" author="shalinmangar" created="Tue, 30 Jun 2015 08:58:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This fix has already been released so I opened &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7736&quot; title=&quot;Add a test for ZkController.publishAndWaitForDownStates&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-7736&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-7736&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to fix the test.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
